About me
Kanagaraj Singaravelu (Professionally known as Kanak)
With over 35 years of cross-functional experience, I bring a unique blend of technical depth and commercial
acumen to every engagement. My career began as a Sales Executive in an IT startup, where I worked closely
with leadership to build the organization from the ground up. Since then, I’ve held strategic roles across sales,
operations, and service delivery—specializing in IT solutions, infrastructure projects, and managed services.
Today, I offer on-demand consulting to startups and mid-sized IT firms—helping them enhance reliability,
reduce operational costs, and scale service delivery. My broad-based expertise enables me to optimize
systems and processes, foster high-performance teams, and empower organizations to make confident, data-
driven decision for sustainable growth.
